    "text": [
        "Dear Sir/Madam,",
        "I am writing this letter with regard to taking part in charity work. I saw a newspaper related to unpaid work with local kids.",
        "I am curious about this work as helping other people always gives me the most satisfaction. I have been working with children for more than five years and I have always felt blessed during this work. Furthermore, I have more patience than youngsters, thus, I can able to an unpaid job with juniors.",
        "I would be grateful if you could give me details of your job.  Can you tell me how many days of the week I could work or for how long each day? Also, I would appreciate it if you could tell me what are the requirements for a non-paid job?",
        "Lastly, I currently work with thousands of students, therefore I am not able to take part in your team until the end of  January month. After this month, I will be available from Monday till Thursday from 8AM to 3PM.",
        "I look forward to hearing from you soon.",
        "Yours sincerely,",
        "Mallika Wadhwa"
